# Growvisi dashboard UI

## Layout

- Shell: `h-dvh`, sidebar fixed, **main column scrolls only** (`dashboard-shell.tsx`)
- Pages: `dashboard-page` wrapper + `PageHeader` (eyebrow, title, description)
- Panels: `DashboardPanel` with staggered `delay` for motion

## Navigation (do not add top-level items casually)

Groups: Overview → Engage → Intelligence → Automate. Settings/Pricing via user menu.

## Product copy in UI

- Conversations page: Meta handles replies; Growvisi = thread + timeline + human takeover (secondary)
- Automations: distinguish server-side (email, stage) vs Meta (welcome)
- Billing: Razorpay, INR, trial banner when `entitlements.requiresUpgrade`
- Empty states: action toward `/onboarding` or `/dashboard/settings#whatsapp`

## Patterns to reuse

- `status-banners.tsx` for deployment/trial/WhatsApp warnings
- `apiFetch` + React Query; invalidate on realtime events
- `brand-copy.ts` for labels — don't hardcode nav strings in pages

## Avoid

- Promising auto-reply from Growvisi
- Legal links duplicated in sidebar (keep in settings/footer)
- Scrollable sidebar tied to main content scroll
- New emoji-heavy or generic "AI magic" marketing inside dashboard
